\begin_inset Formula 
\[
M_{XY}(t,s)={\rm E}(e^{tX+sY})
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Corollary
If 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

 are independent, then 
\begin_inset Formula $M_{XY}(t,s)=M_{X}(t)M_{Y}(s)$
\end_inset

.
