 & =\exp\left\{ \boldsymbol{\mu}^{T}\boldsymbol{A}^{T}\boldsymbol{t}+\frac{1}{2}(\boldsymbol{A}^{T}\boldsymbol{t})^{T}\Sigma(\boldsymbol{A}^{T}\boldsymbol{t})\right\} \\
 & =\exp\left\{ (\boldsymbol{A\mu})^{T}\boldsymbol{t}+\frac{1}{2}\boldsymbol{t}^{T}(\boldsymbol{A}\Sigma\boldsymbol{A}^{T})\boldsymbol{t}\right\} 
\end{align*}

\end_inset

the last expression is the MGF of 
\begin_inset Formula ${\rm N}(\boldsymbol{A\mu},\boldsymbol{A}\Sigma\boldsymbol{A}^{T})$
\end_inset

 distribution.
